structure.unit: A AUTOMATED MOTOR VEHICLE REGISTRATION SYSTEM

law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 128, sec. 14, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 96, effective July 1, 1987. -- Created 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 164, sec. 25, effective July 15, 1982.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Issuance of documents in county not equipped with operable automated system.
